# Documentation
- Document complex logic and non-obvious code decisions.
- Follow official Flutter and Bloc documentation for best practices.
- Document all public APIs with dartdoc comments.
- Maintain architecture decision records (ADRs) for major decisions.
- Create per-feature documentation in docs/features/.
- Document widget hierarchy and theming guidelines.
- Include test coverage reports and patterns.
- Document state management and navigation flows.
- Keep API documentation updated with examples.